## Platform Choice ‚Äî Fourthwall

Everything runs through **Fourthwall** ‚Äî memberships, merch, and the storefront. One platform, one brand experience, one URL.

### Why Fourthwall over Patreon

| Factor | Fourthwall | Patreon |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Platform fee** | 5% + payment processing | 10% standard for new creators + payment processing |
| **Branding** | Fully white-label. Custom domain, your logo, your colors. No platform branding anywhere. | Always patreon.com/username with Patreon's UI and navigation visible. |
| **Merch integration** | Built-in store with print-on-demand, custom products, and member-only discounts per tier. 0% platform fee on physical products. | No native merch store. Third-party add-on costs an additional 3% of all monthly earnings. |
| **Twitch integration** | Twitch Gifting (gift memberships and merch to chat), Twitch subscriber discounts, on-stream alerts via FourthwallHQ bot. | No native Twitch integration whatsoever. |
