## Community Architecture

### Discord ‚Äî The Outside Inn

The Discord server is called **The Outside Inn** ‚Äî the community gathering place within the EIW brand. The inn is the conceptual home: warm, inviting, a place travelers return to. The name carries the investment in custom pixel art and lo-fi atmosphere into the community space itself.

